data.description: Welcome to your perfect oasis, mere moments from the prestigious equestrian center in the heart of Wellington.This move-in ready townhouse is a dream come true, featuring a master bedroom conveniently located downstairs with a walk in tub for effortless living. Step into luxury with a recently remodeled kitchen boasting high-end stone countertops, stunning stainless steel appliances, and an elegant backsplash. The lavish upgrades extend to the remodeled bathrooms and fresh paint throughout, ensuring a chic and contemporary aesthetic.Prepare to be enchanted by the outdoor haven awaiting you, complete with a beautifully landscaped backyard and an extended patio perfect for al fresco dining and entertaining.With the option to purchase fully furnished, this home is truly turnkey and ready to welcome you with open arms. Don't miss out on the opportunity to experience the epitome of comfort and style in Wellington's sought-after community. Schedule your exclusive tour today and make this dream home yours.
